1
00:00:26,210 --> 00:00:28,050
智媛
JI-WON

2
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:36,140
杀了我
Kill me.

3
00:00:48,740 --> 00:00:52,950
我的命运终究是要死在朴敏焕手上吗？
Was I destined to die in Park Min-hwan's hands?

4
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:58,830
智媛
Ji-won.

5
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:01,920
智媛
Ji-won.

6
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:03,830
智媛！
Ji-won!

7
00:01:18,850 --> 00:01:20,730
等等，等一下
Wait. Hold on...

8
00:01:47,290 --> 00:01:48,340
你说一次看看
Tell me again.

9
00:01:52,220 --> 00:01:55,010
我以后不接李在元的电话
I won't answer Lee Jae-won's calls.

10
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:58,100
就算他到家里来，也不要开门
If he comes to the house, I won't open the door,

11
00:01:58,180 --> 00:02:00,180
然后马上打电话给你
and call you right away.

12
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,140
李室长
Mr. Lee.

13
00:02:04,850 --> 00:02:09,070
感谢你每次都载我到医院来
Thank you for driving me to the hospital every time like this

14
00:02:09,690 --> 00:02:12,190
也感谢你和我洽谈离婚事宜…
and giving me divorce advice, but--

15
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,610
你不必感谢我
You don't have to thank me for that.

16
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:16,780
这是我的业务
It's work for me.

17
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:20,450
U&K付我很多钱
I get paid a lot of money from U&K.

18
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:23,540
我只是照着雇主的要求去做
I do what my employer wants.

19
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:29,210
好
Okay.

20
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,970
不过你说过你关心我
But you said you cared about me.

21
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,440
你还是把想说的话都说出来了
You just have to say your piece.

22
00:02:55,570 --> 00:02:56,570
请等一下
Just a moment.

23
00:02:58,370 --> 00:03:00,780
刘志赫部长
GENERAL MANAGER YU JI-HYUK

24
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,830
喂？怎么会这个时间打给我？
Hey, what is it at this hour?

25
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,500
我现在在警察局
I'm at the police station.

26
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:06,710
警察局？
The police station?

27
00:03:09,290 --> 00:03:10,500
我现在马上过去
I'll be right there.

28
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:13,090
不用到这里来，请你到医院去
No, go to the hospital instead.

29
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:15,630
唯一医院
YUIL MEDICAL CENTER

30
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,930
第15集
EPISODE 15

31
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,550
区域紧急医疗中心

32
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,640
不好意思
Excuse me.

33
00:03:23,770 --> 00:03:27,690
姜智媛，32岁，从江南的U&K总公司送过来的这位患者在哪里？
Kang Ji-won, 32, transferred from U&K in Gangnam. Where is she?

34
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:31,020
亲爱的
Ji-won.

35
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,860
她的呼吸和脉搏都恢复正常了
Her breathing and pulse are stable now.

36
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:38,740
稍微有点发烧，等她恢复意识，我们会再过来看看
But she has a fever, so we'll check her once she wakes up.

37
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:43,370
由于是暴力事件，她跟警察一起过来，我开诊断书给你们
It was an assault, so she came with the police. I'll get you her record.

38
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:51,540
喂
Hey.

39
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:54,170
我会终结你的人生
I'm going to ruin your life,

40
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,050
做好心理准备
so brace yourself.

41
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:59,930
我会向媒体爆料富三代施暴又仗势欺人
I'll tell the media a third-generation tycoon assaulted me.

42
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:03,890
现在这个时代，你隐瞒不了的
You can't cover things up these days.

43
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:07,310
我已经惨到不能再惨了
I have nothing to lose now.

44
00:04:08,850 --> 00:04:09,900
都是因为你
Thanks to you.

45
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:15,360
为了姜智媛而毁了你的人生会不会太逊了？
But isn't Ji-won too inferior to ruin your life over?

46
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,450
她瘦巴巴的，有什么看头？
She's nothing but skin and bones.

47
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,620
刘部长
Mr. Yu.

48
00:04:25,910 --> 00:04:27,160
要我给你一个忠告吗？
Do you want some advice?

49
00:04:28,290 --> 00:04:29,540
不要太相信她
Don't trust her.

50
00:04:31,170 --> 00:04:32,790
你知道我为何会疯掉吗？
Do you know why I went mad?

51
00:04:33,380 --> 00:04:35,920
姜智媛会让人发疯
Ji-won makes people lose their minds.

52
00:04:37,050 --> 00:04:39,760
毁掉你的不是我和姜智媛
Ji-won and I aren't the ones that ruined you.

53
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,680
是你的垃圾品行
It's your trashy personality.

54
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:48,140
把人打成这样，你的品行就很高尚吗？
Look how you beat me. Is your personality any better?

55
00:04:48,770 --> 00:04:51,520
你不能因为比我会打架就这样
You can't do this because you fight better.

56
00:04:52,770 --> 00:04:56,900
你才是不该那样对待体重只有你一半的女人吧？
That's a bit rich, considering what you did to a woman half your size.

57
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:58,900
什么？
What?

58
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:06,160
对你不利的时候，你就寻求平等
You seek equality when at a disadvantage,

59
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,410
对你有利的时候，你就爱展现力量
and strength when at an advantage.

60
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:14,290
其实我不喜欢运用我的力量
I hate using my strength.

61
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,590
可是对你，我不得不用
But not to you.

62
00:05:21,970 --> 00:05:23,550
刘志赫先生，请出来
Mr. Yu, you can come out.

63
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,640
走吧
Let's go.

64
00:05:29,810 --> 00:05:31,060
那我呢？
What about me?

65
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:32,900
为什么不把我弄出去？
Why can't I come out?

66
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:36,320
我呢？
What about me?

67
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:39,860
你以为你的人生不能再惨了吗？
Do you really think you can't go any lower?

68
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:45,450
大错特错
You're wrong.

69
00:05:51,370 --> 00:05:53,500
不，为什么只有有钱人可以出去？
No, wait. Is it because he's rich?

70
00:05:54,210 --> 00:05:55,380
我也是U&K的人
I work at U&K too!

71
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:57,340
那我呢？
What about me?

72
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:02,050
有钱没罪，没钱有罪！
One law for the rich and another for the poor!

73
00:06:05,470 --> 00:06:07,510
朴敏焕从今天起被解雇
Min-hwan is fired as of today

74
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:10,600
事由是对同事施暴，违反公司规定
for assaulting a colleague and violating the rules.

75
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,810
也再找找其他事由
Find anything else.

76
00:06:11,890 --> 00:06:13,850
上次出轨事件时，我有查过了
I checked during his affair incident.

77
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:16,730
他还有擅离职守、使用公司信用卡明细不清
AWOL and unclear corporate card statements.

78
00:06:16,810 --> 00:06:18,770
不当招待厂商的情况
And he illegally treated clients.

79
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:21,740
很好，他是不是有公司贷款？
Good. Doesn't he have a company loan?

80
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:24,400
我会要银行向他提出还款要求
I'll ask the bank for a repayment request.

81
00:06:24,490 --> 00:06:27,410
我会把暴力、伤害等可以加的罪名都加上去
I'll add assault, injury, and anything else.

82
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:29,330
还有姜智媛…
And Ms. Kang is...

83
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:33,000
她现在在家里
She's at home.

84
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:35,710
这是她的意愿
It's what she wanted.

85
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:38,090
我刚好和杨珠兰科长在一起
I happened to be with Ms. Yang.

86
00:06:38,170 --> 00:06:42,050
所以我让杨科长去陪她，不过她看起来不太好
So I left Ms. Kang with her, but she didn't look good.

87
00:06:48,220 --> 00:06:51,890
朴敏焕是不是也有欠高利贷没还？
You said there was a debt that Min-hwan hadn't paid off, right?

88
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:55,140
施压要他还钱
Put some pressure on that.

89
00:06:55,230 --> 00:06:56,940
我们买下债权也可以
Or buy the bonds.

90
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,110
我马上去查
I'll look into it.

91
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:06,070
刘部长
Mr. Yu.

92
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:09,070
智媛怎么样了？
How's Ji-won?

93
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:11,870
她不太好
She's not good.

94
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:16,500
我想她睡一觉会比较好，所以想让她喝点牛奶
I think she'll be better if she sleeps, so I'll get her some milk.

95
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,380
可是家里什么都没有
There's nothing in her house.

96
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:21,420
部长，你还好吗？
Are you okay?

97
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:24,340
嗯，还好
Well, yes.

98
00:07:25,130 --> 00:07:29,180
谢谢你，现在由我来接手，你回去休息吧
Thank you. I'll take it from here. You should go home and rest.

99
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,630
志赫
Ji-hyuk.

100
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:16,310
对不起
I'm sorry.

101
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:20,440
全都是我不好
I'm sorry for everything.

102
00:08:28,900 --> 00:08:30,490
你有没有受伤？
Were you hurt?

103
00:08:31,410 --> 00:08:32,570
这边怎么了？
What's this?

104
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:01,040
你好
Hello.

105
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,210
问候就只有这样？
Is that all?

106
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:08,670
也太少了吧
It can't be.

107
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:13,680
你打来是因为你先生受我照顾
Considering you called because your husband's in my care,

108
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,300
只说这样也太少了吧
there should be more.

109
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:26,690
你们要不要到中国去一阵子？
How about going to China for a while?

110
00:10:26,770 --> 00:10:32,320
唉唷，那我们当然感激不尽
Oh, my. We would be so thankful if you could do that for us.

111
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,740
不过你们搭船的时候，会有些辛苦
It'll be a rough ride on the ship though.

112
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:39,580
唉唷，那怎么会辛苦呢？我们都没把您吩咐的事给办好
That's nothing at all. We couldn't even get the job done.

113
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:42,080
如果您再给我一次机会
If you give us another chance,

114
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:45,040
我会用力踩油门，把她辗过去
I'll hit the accelerator and crush her.

115
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,790
请一定要联络我
So just let me know.

116
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:47,920
好，谢谢
Yeah, thank you.

117
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:52,920
没钱的人总会试图留下些东西
Poor people always try to keep a record.

118
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:57,340
手上必须要握有保险
As insurance.

119
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:00,560
你想要的是什么？
What do you want?

120
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:06,400
你不喜欢我好好照顾你爸吗？
Do you hate that I'm taking care of your father?

121
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:11,440
只要把姜智媛辗过去的简单事情变得不再简单了
Now that crushing Kang Ji-won isn't so simple anymore,

122
00:11:11,530 --> 00:11:14,570
你就突然要我们什么都别做
you suddenly say, "Don't do anything."

123
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:19,450
之后朴敏换还突然说要离婚
Then Park Min-hwan suddenly asks me for a divorce,

124
00:11:20,370 --> 00:11:23,080
而我爸又不接电话，我就明白了
and my dad won't pick up, so I realize,

125
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,750
这样下去，只有我会完蛋
"I'll get screwed over."

126
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:32,210
从你的表情看来
Judging by the look on your face,

127
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:36,260
有钱人也没多厉害
you're nothing special.

128
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:41,640
可恶，我不该窝在房间里的
Darn it. Why have I been cooped up at home like that?

129
00:11:43,850 --> 00:11:45,310
换我问问题了
I ask the questions now.

130
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:47,140
你能为我做什么？
What can you do for me?

131
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:59,450
韩国的小虾米是有毒吗？怎么会这么没有分寸？
Are the shrimps in Korea poisonous? Why don't they know their place?

132
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:08,210
郑万植和裴熙淑的尸体被发现了吗？
Have the bodies of Jeong Man-sik and Bae Hui-suk been found?

133
00:12:08,290 --> 00:12:10,000
我会去查警方的报告
I'll check the police report.

134
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:16,840
暂时不要让新闻报出来
Make sure there's no news about it.

135
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:21,220
让郑秀敏感到有危机变得没好处了
Jeong Su-min shouldn't feel threatened now.

136
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:24,760
朴敏焕和郑秀敏
Park Min-hwan and Jeong Su-min.

137
00:12:24,850 --> 00:12:27,520
可以一次解决掉吗？
Can we take care of them both at once?

138
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:36,440
朴敏焕
PARK MIN-HWAN

139
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:40,910
喂？
Hello?

140
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:42,990
我现在在警察局
I'm at the police station right now.

141
00:12:43,070 --> 00:12:45,950
不好意思，可以请你帮个忙吗？
I'm sorry, but can I ask for a favor?

142
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:48,710
什么？警察局？
What? The police station?

143
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:49,750
首尔城三警察局
SUNGSAM POLICE STATION

144
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:52,170
虽然把你弄出来了，但是这个案子有些严重
We got you out, but it's pretty serious.

145
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:54,790
我们可能罩不了你
We may not be able to cover it.

146
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:57,170
什么？那是什么意思？
What? What are you saying?

147
00:12:57,920 --> 00:13:00,180
你没有事先跟我们商量过，就做出这种行为
It wasn't what we agreed on.

148
00:13:00,970 --> 00:13:05,060
若我们与U&K正面对决，副社长的负担会很大
If we have to fight U&K head-on, the burden on Ms. Oh will be big.

149
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,140
喂！
Hey!

150
00:13:06,890 --> 00:13:10,140
你那是什么讲话态度？你以为你是谁啊？
What's with the attitude? Who do you think you are?

151
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:12,400
你是云彩航空的副社长吗？
You're not the VP of Cloud Air!

152
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:19,530
喂
Hey.

153
00:13:19,610 --> 00:13:20,950
你也不是
You're not either.

154
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:22,910
所以不要这么没礼貌
So don't be rude.

155
00:13:25,950 --> 00:13:26,990
可恶
Damn it.

156
00:13:28,660 --> 00:13:31,870
只在擂台上打架的家伙，就只会耍嘴皮子
You only know how to fight in the ring. Watch your mouth.

157
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,710
你不过就是吴宥拉的小喽罗
You're just Yu-ra's henchman.

158
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:36,250
还敢对我颐指气使
Don't act like you're my boss.

159
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:37,840
混账
Bastard.

160
00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:42,550
先生，等一下
Mister, wait!

161
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:46,930
你为什么要把他打到流鼻血？
Why would you give him a nosebleed?

162
00:13:47,010 --> 00:13:48,970
我有什么理由不能那么做吗？
Is there a reason I can't?

163
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:51,270
那家伙的态度很糟糕啊！
He gave me attitude!

164
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:53,100
可恶
Damn it...

165
00:13:53,190 --> 00:13:55,020
他只是太过担心我了
He's just worried about me.

166
00:13:55,110 --> 00:13:58,150
今天你老婆来威胁我
Since your wife came and threatened me today.

167
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:01,190
很可怕
It was scary.

168
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:03,820
什么？威胁什呢？
What? About what?

169
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:07,200
她说你要离婚，她不愿意自己一个人死
She said you asked for a divorce. She won't go down alone.

170
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:10,620
她说不会让你独自脱身
She won't let you get away alone.

171
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,040
她疯啦？真是的
Is she out of her mind? Damn it.

172
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:16,170
等等
Hold on.

173
00:14:16,250 --> 00:14:17,750
U&K人事总管
U&K HR DEPARTMENT

174
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:21,670
我公司打电话来了，先挂电话吧，我等一下再打给你
Work's calling me. Hang up. I'll call you back later.

175
00:14:24,130 --> 00:14:25,140
喂？
Hello?

176
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:28,510
朴敏焕先生，我要通知你，你从今天起被解雇了
Mr. Park, I called to say you're fired as of today.

177
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,720
由于你目前没有来上班
You didn't come to work today,

178
00:14:30,810 --> 00:14:35,560
因此法务组已经派人递交书面解雇通知书到你府上
so the legal team has sent someone to deliver your written dismissal.

179
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,610
你在哪里？
Where are you?

180
00:14:40,690 --> 00:14:44,320
你公司有人过来，你怎么会被解雇？
Someone from your workplace is here. You're fired?

181
