- Doctor. - Are you drunk?

227
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:53,260
医师，我是她的丈夫
I'm her husband.

228
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:57,100
可是她躲在这里，也不接电话
But she was hiding here and ignoring my calls.

229
