行车纪录器？
The dashcam recording?

236
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:16,240
没有影像的那个？
There's no video.

237
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,370
珠兰
Ju-ran.

238
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:23,870
大姐！
Ju-ran!

239
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:29,300
你没办法用那个跟我离婚
You can't divorce me with that!

240
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:32,170
要看得到画面，让人无法抵赖
You must have the video. Hard evidence.

241
00:18:32,260 --> 00:18:34,090
- 请你出去 - 不要拦我
- Let's get you outside. - Come on.

242
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:37,390
你要让妍芝没有爸爸吗？
Yeon-ji will be fatherless because of you.

243
00:18:42,930 --> 00:18:45,690
你是谁？搞什么？放开我！
Who are you? What's going on? Let go!

244
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:48,900
你没有认真看离婚诉状
Did you even read the divorce papers?

245
00:18:50,690 --> 00:18:51,610
李锡俊
Lee Seok-jun.

246
00:18:52,650 --> 00:18:54,360
我是杨珠兰的律师
I'm Ms. Yang Ju-ran's lawyer.

247
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:56,570
律师？
Lawyer?

248
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:58,530
我会声请保护令
I'll apply for a restraining order.

249
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:04,120
不要再来了
Never come back.

250
00:19:08,210 --> 00:19:09,250
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

251
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:10,920
嗯
Yes.

252
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:16,180
负责手术的医师很有实力，又有自信
The doctor is good and confident about the surgery,

253
00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:18,050
- 你不用太担心 - 对了
- so don't worry. - Right.

254
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:19,720
智媛还好吗？
Is Ji-won okay?

255
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:26,060
据我所知，她没事
As far as I know, yes.

256
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:32,690
不过请你也担心一下自己
But you should worry about yourself.

257
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:46,330
好久不见了
It's been a while.

258
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:51,130
我很惊讶你会突然联络我
I was so surprised to get your call.

259
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:55,550
许久不见，见到你真高兴
It's nice to see you after so long.

260
00:19:56,470 --> 00:19:57,840
要点餐吗？
Can I take your order?

261
00:19:59,300 --> 00:20:00,430
你过得好吗？
Have you been well?

262
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:03,640
嗯，过得很好
Yes, I have.

263
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:13,150
其实我过得不好
To be honest, I'm not doing that well.

264
00:20:14,730 --> 00:20:19,160
朴敏换和我决定要离婚了
Min-hwan and I are getting a divorce.

265
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:22,490
昨天我离开家里，现在住在楼上
I left the house yesterday. I'm staying upstairs.

266
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:24,240
想休息一阵子
I'm going to rest for now.

267
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:29,830
这是因果报应
It must be karma.

268
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:36,420
我被爱情蒙蔽了双眼
Blinded by love, I betrayed

269
00:20:37,170 --> 00:20:39,010
背叛了我唯一的闺蜜，我的另一半
my only best friend.

270
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,890
结果…
In the end...

271
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:48,980
总之我现在是一个人了
Anyway, I'm all alone now.

272
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,900
你说你要离婚，那事情变得容易许多
The divorce makes this easier to say.

273
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:00,450
你打算要杀了姜智媛吧？
Did you try to kill Ji-won?

274
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,460
换作是我也会这么做
I would've done the same.

275
00:21:15,420 --> 00:21:18,130
我的意思是说 我知道姜智媛和朴敏焕
I'm saying I know Ji-won and Min-hwan are

276
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:21,260
又重新在一起了
seeing each other again.

277
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:24,430
他们两个…
Are they really...

278
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:27,560
真的重新在一起了？
seeing each other again?

279
00:21:32,230 --> 00:21:34,360
告他们通奸罪吧
Let's charge them with adultery.

280
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:39,030
我会告诉你何时跟如何进去
I'll let you know when and where to go.

281
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,780
如果你有需要的话 我也会帮你找最好的律师
If you want, I'll get you the best lawyer too.

282
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:47,330
你就只需履行身为法定配偶的权利
You just fulfill your role as his legal spouse.

283
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,080
为什么要帮我？
Why?

284
00:21:56,250 --> 00:21:57,590
我不服气
Because it's not fair.

285
00:21:58,670 --> 00:22:01,470
你的人生不是由于朴敏焕而毁了吗？
Isn't your life ruined because of Min-hwan?

286
00:22:05,340 --> 00:22:09,390
要是你离婚 你就拿不到之前在公司工作的补偿
If you divorce, you won't be rewarded for your work at the company.

287
00:22:10,220 --> 00:22:11,850
你什么都不剩
You'll be left with nothing.

288
00:22:12,850 --> 00:22:13,850
我…
That's true...

289
00:22:15,150 --> 00:22:16,400
的确是如此
for me.

290
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:21,280
那你能得到什么？
But what do you gain?

291
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:34,830
我希望姜智媛回到我身边
I want to get Kang Ji-won back.

292
00:22:38,290 --> 00:22:39,920
我喜欢姜智媛
I like Ji-won.

293
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,880
所以我讨厌她跟朴敏焕纠缠
So I hate that she's with him.

294
00:22:46,140 --> 00:22:48,760
我会想办法让她回到我身边
I'm going to make her come back to me.

295
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,680
所以帮帮我
So help me.

296
00:23:06,490 --> 00:23:07,990
我可以问你一件事吗？
Can I ask you something?

297
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,210
你为什么讨厌我？
Why do you hate me?

298
00:23:20,380 --> 00:23:21,800
因为你只知道自己
Because you're selfish.

299
00:23:23,050 --> 00:23:25,970
有的人会啃食身边的人
There are those who gnaw at people around them.

300
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:30,810
而你正是这种人，所以我很讨厌
You are that type, so I hate you.

301
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:35,310
你又不了解我
You don't know me that well.

302
00:23:35,390 --> 00:23:37,230
你不相信任何人吧？
You don't trust anyone, do you?

303
00:23:38,230 --> 00:23:40,480
那是因为你是不值得信任的人
That's because you're not trustworthy.

304
00:23:42,610 --> 00:23:46,780
你认为别人也跟你一样 所以你无法相信人
You think everyone's like you, so you can't trust anyone.

305
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:51,740
你这么想，我们怎么合作？
How can you work with me thinking like that?

306
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:56,210
你不是问我为什么讨厌你吗？
Didn't you ask me why I hated you?

307
00:23:56,710 --> 00:23:58,960
我没说我无法与你合作
I never said I couldn't work with you.

308
00:24:01,670 --> 00:24:03,340
你决定好就告诉我
Let me know when you decide.

309
00:24:13,430 --> 00:24:15,470
谈得很顺利
It went well.

310
00:24:15,560 --> 00:24:19,060
如你所说，她问我为何要帮她
As you said, she asked me why I was helping her.

311
00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:24,980
如果我全都说谎，她应该不会相信 所以我适当地掺入一些真话
I didn't think she'd believe me if I lied, so I mixed in some truth.

312
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:34,490
除了她会发现出轨的一对 是吴宥拉和朴敏焕之外
Except that it'll be Oh Yu-ra and Park Min-hwan instead,

313
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:36,370
我说的全都是事实
everything I said was true.

314
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:38,250
还有…
Also...

315
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:43,420
我们公司有提供给员工一项保险
There's an insurance policy provided to company employees.

316
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,630
家人保险
A family insurance.

317
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:49,010
理赔对象包括本人、配偶与直系血亲
It compensates yourself, spouse, and immediate family.

318
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:52,140
离职时，本人可以决定是否继续加保
You can decide to keep it when you quit.

319
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:53,350
二手市场
SECOND HAND MARKET

320
00:24:53,430 --> 00:24:56,220
过不久应该就会通知朴敏焕
A notice will go to Park Min-hwan soon.

321
00:25:00,850 --> 00:25:05,020
把这个卖了，就可以救急
I can take care of the more urgent debt if this gets sold.

322
00:25:06,860 --> 00:25:09,490
他本来不晓得有这种保险
He doesn't know such insurance existed,

323
00:25:09,570 --> 00:25:11,110
不过很快就会知道了
but he will soon.

324
00:25:12,620 --> 00:25:14,080
舞台正在搭建中
The stage is being set.

325
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:16,200
糖果

326
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:44,020
我要不要干脆去死？
Shall I just die?

327
00:25:44,560 --> 00:25:48,150
虽然如果朴敏换没有起歹念 那项保险就没有用
Though it's useless if Min-hwan doesn't decide to die.

328
00:25:48,230 --> 00:25:49,490
要是我死了
If I die...

329
00:25:52,660 --> 00:25:55,620
我爸妈就能领到我的身故保险金
my mom and dad can get my life insurance benefit.

330
00:25:59,290 --> 00:26:03,120
在朴敏焕走到现在这步之前 有好几次机会可以停止
Min-hwan could've stopped several times on his way here,

331
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:05,790
但是他都没有
but he didn't.

332
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,590
他应该会一路走到底
He'll go all the way.

333
00:26:10,800 --> 00:26:12,220
那就没有问题了
Then there's no problem.

334
00:26:13,050 --> 00:26:15,260
郑秀敏应该也会一路走到底
Jeong Su-min will go all the way too.

335
00:26:20,430 --> 00:26:22,390
为什么大家
Why is everyone

336
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,270
都只在找姜智媛？
looking for Kang Ji-won?

337
00:26:26,190 --> 00:26:29,610
因为现在的郑秀敏 应该会对你更加执着
I think Jeong Su-min is more obsessed with you right now.

338
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:35,990
现在就剩那一刻了
It's that moment now.

339
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:42,750
剩下的就是让郑秀敏经历那一刻
All that's left is for her to experience it.

340
00:27:04,190 --> 00:27:06,150
要不要回日本呢？
How about returning to Japan?

341
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:11,400
比起以前，刘志赫行动积极许多
Yu Ji-hyuk is moving more actively than before.

342
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:13,490
他把朴敏焕个人的债务和高利贷
He's pressuring Park Min-hwan

343
00:27:13,570 --> 00:27:16,700
