with his debt and private loans. He won't last long.

344
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:19,950
他似乎也不放弃寻找郑万植和裴熙淑
And he hasn't given up on Man-sik and Hui-suk.

345
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:23,290
他搜遍了 仁川所有废弃工厂附近的监视器画面
He got all the CCTV footage from the abandoned factory.

346
00:27:23,370 --> 00:27:24,830
虽然他不会找到什么
He won't find anything,

347
00:27:24,910 --> 00:27:28,040
但是与U&K正面迎战，没有任何好处
but nothing good can come from fighting U&K head-on.

348
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:38,260
看来你没信心
You must not be confident.

349
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:41,100
你已经先害怕，要我逃跑了
Seeing how you're telling me to run away.

350
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:45,270
没关系
It's okay.

351
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:49,480
他爷爷不一样
His grandfather is different.

352
00:27:50,770 --> 00:27:53,900
他与温室花朵刘志赫不一样
Unlike Ji-hyuk, who's like a flower in a green house,

353
00:27:53,980 --> 00:27:55,570
他是很现实的人
he's realistic.

354
00:27:56,150 --> 00:28:00,370
他知道灰姑娘会多么令人头疼
He knows how much of a nuisance Cinderella can be.

355
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,100
将军
Checkmate.

356
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:26,020
我都赢不过爷爷
I can never beat you.

357
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:29,400
因为你全都想要，就被我看穿步数了
You want everything, so I can read your hand.

358
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:34,440
懂得放弃不属于自己的东西 是作为领导者的条件
A good leader should know how to give up something that's not theirs.

359
00:28:35,650 --> 00:28:36,820
好
Okay.

360
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,200
你来啦？
Hey!

361
00:28:43,700 --> 00:28:44,830
嗯
Hi.

362
00:28:44,910 --> 00:28:46,910
我和爷爷在下象棋
We were just playing janggi.

363
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,750
今天我又输了
And I lost again.

364
00:28:49,790 --> 00:28:53,460
不过我觉得我应该能赢过你 要一起下吗？
But I think I can beat you. Do you want to play?

365
00:28:55,550 --> 00:28:56,550
爷爷
Grandfather.

366
00:28:56,630 --> 00:28:58,920
您不是要我带喜欢的女生回来吗？
You asked me to bring the woman I like.

367
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:02,140
我会正式带她过来
I will introduce her to you.

368
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:06,140
所以请不要再让宥拉到家里来了
So don't let Yu-ra into the house anymore.

369
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:10,270
你之前说你是单恋，没打算跟她交往
You said it was one-sided and weren't going to make it work.

370
00:29:10,350 --> 00:29:11,850
你改变心意了吗？
Did you change your mind?

371
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:14,060
对，我打算跟她在一起
Yes, I'm going to pursue it.

372
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:18,570
可是家里不能有前未婚妻进出
So I can't have my ex-fiancée frequenting my house.

373
00:29:22,360 --> 00:29:25,200
我在订婚期间太不用心了
I was so indifferent during our engagement.

374
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:28,500
我都不晓得他这么急性子
I didn't know he was so impatient.

375
00:29:28,580 --> 00:29:30,500
像我们这样的人
People like us

376
00:29:30,580 --> 00:29:33,330
结婚不是我们说好就可以
can't marry for love, can we?

377
00:29:34,130 --> 00:29:37,340
别做鲁莽的举动 先获得爷爷的同意…
Get permission from your grandfather before you--

378
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:38,260
我会的
I will.

379
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:40,800
我现在就把她介绍给您
I'll introduce her now.

380
00:29:58,690 --> 00:30:01,110
您好，我是姜智媛
Hello, I'm Kang Ji-won.

381
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:15,380
我们来把姜智媛处理掉
Let's get rid of Kang Ji-won.

382
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:18,210
你不要回日本吗？
You're not going back to Japan?

383
00:30:18,300 --> 00:30:20,380
我输了会活不下去
I can't live with myself if I lose.

384
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:24,430
我为何要被微不足道的小虫 害得我有这种感觉？
Why do I have to feel this way over those cockroaches?

385
00:30:25,510 --> 00:30:28,600
对，当初我就应该亲自出手
Yeah, I should've done it myself.

386
00:30:29,100 --> 00:30:31,350
借他人之手只是让自己头痛
It's a headache having others do it.

387
00:30:48,580 --> 00:30:52,660
我告诉自己 必然会发生的事，就算困难也要面对
I've decided to face the obstacles that are bound to happen.

388
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:04,170
上次我跟你见面的时候
When I met you last time,

389
00:31:05,300 --> 00:31:08,100
有些话没有告诉你
there's something I didn't tell you.

390
00:31:09,890 --> 00:31:13,770
并不是面对就能解决所有事情
Powering through isn't a solution to everything.

391
00:31:15,060 --> 00:31:19,320
我知道我孙子给了你 许多作为短暂交往的回报
I'm aware he gave you a lot for seeing him briefly.

392
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:22,990
所以你以后打算怎么做？
So what are you going to do from now on?

393
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:26,860
我会回过头去看和反省我有没有做错
I'll look back and reflect on my faults.

394
00:31:27,490 --> 00:31:29,450
能够改正的就改正
I'll correct what I can.

395
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:31,160
剩下的…
And the rest...

396
00:31:32,870 --> 00:31:35,040
我想我也无可奈何
I guess it is what it is.

397
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:42,090
现在差不多是你想你也无可奈何 然后退出的时候了
It's time for you to step back and say, "It is what it is."

398
00:31:46,430 --> 00:31:48,260
您果然知道这件事
So you knew.

399
00:31:52,970 --> 00:31:55,310
我为了这件事狠狠骂了刘志赫
I gave him hell for that.

400
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:58,600
不会再有这种事了
That won't ever happen again.

401
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:03,730
他真的有很多不足
He lacks so much.

402
00:32:05,690 --> 00:32:07,450
您对他娇生惯养
You spoiled him.

403
00:32:07,530 --> 00:32:10,870
他只知道工作，对钱完全没有概念
He only knows how to work. He has no concept of money.

404
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:15,870
