What are you trying to say?

406
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:26,510
可是我喜欢他这一点
But I liked that about him.

407
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:31,260
其实我也是有很多不足的人
To tell you the truth, I lack a lot too.

408
00:32:32,930 --> 00:32:36,560
当我以为他是完美的富三代的时候
When I thought he was a perfect third-generation chaebol,

409
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:39,060
