he seemed unreachable.

410
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:45,190
可是当我看到他傻气、生气、散漫
But he can be foolish, get angry, and messy.

411
00:32:46,070 --> 00:32:48,280
不知所措，以及有时…
He gets embarrassed, and sometimes...

412
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:52,620
耍孩子气的样子
he acts like a baby. Seeing those sides of him,

413
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:58,960
我想我们可以好好在一起
I thought we could do well together.

414
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:08,470
我想要跟他一起过得幸福
I want to be happy with him.

415
00:33:12,430 --> 00:33:13,510
