Your husband was fired.

476
00:37:57,210 --> 00:38:01,470
所以别在这里无谓地怀疑我 回去当个贤内助，对哦
So stop suspecting me, and go be a good wife. Oh, wait.

477
00:38:01,970 --> 00:38:03,260
你们要离婚了吧？
You two are divorcing.

478
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:06,680
真糟糕
That's too bad.

479
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,230
不过…
But...

480
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:13,230
我越想越觉得不高兴
thinking about it is pissing me off.

481
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:17,650
只有你才会贪图朴敏焕这种垃圾
Only you would covet trash like Min-hwan.

482
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,650
我怎么会呢？
Why would I?

483
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:25,370
除非我是个傻子才会吧
Unless I was a fool.

484
00:38:35,290 --> 00:38:38,340
放手，我自己走，放开我！
Let go. I'm going. Let me go!

485
00:38:45,470 --> 00:38:49,850
敏焕，刚才郑秀敏来公司大闹 吓到我了
Min-hwan, Jeong Su-min just came and caused a fuss. It scared me.

486
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:56,690
不过公司不会谣传什么八卦 因为大家都只在说郑秀敏是不是疯了
But rumors won't spread here since everyone thinks Su-min's crazy.

487
00:38:58,860 --> 00:39:01,860
唉呀，不小心传错了，抱歉
Oh, no. I sent it to the wrong person. Sorry.

488
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:05,030
她真的是疯了！
Is she out of her mind?

489
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:10,160
我不会放过她
I won't stand for this.

490
